en_890944_0	Minister Gamini Jayawickrema Perera says that legal action will be taken against those who distort and disrespect Buddhism.
en_890944_1	He said this to the media after meeting the Mahanayakas of the Malwathu and Asgiri Chapters.
en_890944_2	Minister Gamini Jayawickrema Perera met the Maha Nayaka of Malwathu Chapter Most Venerable Thibbotuwawe Sri Sumangala Thera at the Malwathu Maha Vihara.
en_890944_3	Thereafter he called on the Maha Nayaka of Asgiri Chapter Most Venerable Warakagoda Sri Gnanarathana Thera.
en_890944_4	The Minister briefed the Maha Nayakas about the proposed programs for the betterment of the Buddhasasana.
